              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26178670/" class="">第195页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3451746/" class=" " title="Anne">Anne</a>
                (生活带我去哪里,我就去哪里.)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="26178670">
